<title>Sonny's Pizza & Pasta - San Clemente, California - Authentic Italian Food</title>
<meta name="keywords" content="Pizza, restaurant, pasta, san clemente, california, food, italian food, dining">
<meta name="description" content="Sonny's Pizza and Pasta Italian Restaurant, located in San Clemente ca., serves authentic food made from scratch fresh everyday,
in a romantic atmosphere with patio dining. ">
</head>

